snippet.title: Animal Crossing: NEW MURDER | Trailer
snippet.description:
Are you a fan of solving murder mysteries and own a copy of Animal Crossing: New Horizons? What about talking to fun characters while hunting for clues? Boy, I got a game for you!

Animal Crossing: NEW MURDER!

ACNM is a Ace-Attorney-esque who-dun-it fan game inspired by Animal Crossing! 

Go to the website to learn more and to play!
www.acnewmurder.com
